---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Halmetoja Model — Structural Theory of Regulation" description="A structural framework for understanding identity, regulation, and relational asymmetry.">

  <main class="home">

    {/* HERO */}
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>The Halmetoja Model</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        A structural theory of regulation, orientation, and relational cost.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="/halmetoja-model/" class="btn-primary">
          Explore the Framework →
        </a>
        <a href="/halmetoja-model/positioning/" class="btn-secondary">
          Positioning Statement
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* WHAT IT IS */}
    <section class="section">
      <h2>What This Site Is</h2>
      <p>
        This is not a self-help site.
        It does not offer personality quizzes.
        It does not assign moral villains.
      </p>
      <p>
        It provides a structural map of how regulation settles under constraint —
        and how relational asymmetry becomes stable.
      </p>
    </section>

    {/* CORE TOPICS */}
    <section class="section">
      <h2>Core Framework</h2>

      <div class="grid">

        <a class="card" href="/halmetoja-model/center-orbit-model/">
          <h3>CENTER–ORBIT Model</h3>
          <p>Two regulatory orientations. One structural axis.</p>
        </a>

        <a class="card" href="/halmetoja-model/narcissism-explained/">
          <h3>Narcissism Explained</h3>
          <p>Narcissism as regulatory configuration — not moral defect.</p>
        </a>

        <a class="card" href="/halmetoja-model/empath-narcissist-dynamic/">
          <h3>Empath–Narcissist Dynamic</h3>
          <p>Why the loop forms. Why it stabilizes. Why it persists.</p>
        </a>

        <a class="card" href="/halmetoja-model/shadow-integration/">
          <h3>Shadow & Integration</h3>
          <p>A structural reinterpretation of Jung’s shadow.</p>
        </a>

        <a class="card" href="/halmetoja-model/metrics/">
          <h3>The Four Metrics</h3>
          <p>CTO, AI, RSR, IRS — locating structure without blame.</p>
        </a>

      </div>
    </section>

    {/* BOOKS / PROJECTS */}
    <section class="section">
      <h2>Books & Projects</h2>
      <p>
        The theoretical framework informs ongoing writing projects exploring
        relational systems, integration, and cultural structure.
      </p>

      <a href="/projects/" class="link">
        View Projects →
      </a>
    </section>

    {/* FOOTNOTE */}
    <section class="section subtle">
      <p>
        Clarity reduces confusion.
        It does not guarantee comfort.
      </p>
    </section>

  </main>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .home {
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 4rem;
  }

  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    padding: 0.8rem 1.4rem;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    padding: 0.8rem 1.4rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.2rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .card {
    display: block;
    padding: 1.4rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--text);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
    transition: border 0.2s ease;
  }

  .card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .card p {
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .link {
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .subtle {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.3rem;
    }
  }
</style>